            turn orange-brown in the fall, the Bald Cypress is a durable, hardy
            tree that grows well in a variety of soil types. Ideal for areas
            that may experience seasonal flooding or near water features.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="tree-option">
          <a href="/cedar-elm">
            <h3>Cedar Elm</h3>
          </a>
